{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775855944275,"sessionID":"ses_286bec61bffehSsgEPkoMRhDU8","part":{"id":"prt_d79419a2b0010mBY34Ew6hfcIf","messageID":"msg_d79418c27001ALc1R3MddFOTBb","sessionID":"ses_286bec61bffehSsgEPkoMRhDU8","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_fc5c352ef4124e3c91cda251","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore invoke/status source code","prompt":"I need to understand the actual implementation of the invoke and status commands in the agentcube CLI project. Please explore the following files and return their full contents:\n\n1. Find and read `cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py` - look for invoke() and status() functions\n2. Find and read `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py` - full InvokeRuntime class\n3. Find and read `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` - full StatusRuntime class\n4. Find and read `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py` - especially get_agent_runtime method\n5. Find and read `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py` - especially get_agent_status method\n6. Find and read any test files related to invoke or status commands\n\nAlso check if there are any existing tests for these commands.\n\nReturn the full file contents for each file found, along with the file paths.","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_286be54ceffeYl7uK1tpbR3xQ7 (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nNow I have a complete picture. Here is my comprehensive findings report:\n\n---\n\n## Summary: Invoke and Status Commands in AgentCube CLI\n\n### Key Finding: These commands are NOT YET IMPLEMENTED\n\nThe `invoke` and `status` commands, along with their runtime classes (`InvokeRuntime`, `StatusRuntime`), are **planned but not implemented**. They exist only in specification/design documents and task lists. All tasks in `changes/AR-023/tasks.md` are unchecked.\n\n---\n\n## Files That EXIST (with full contents already returned above)\n\n### 1. `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/cli/main.py`\n**Status:** EXISTS - but only contains `pack`, `build`, and `publish` commands. No `invoke()` or `status()` functions.\n- 205 lines total\n- Uses Typer framework\n- Has `_handle_error()` helper function that invoke/status would reuse\n\n### 2. `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/services/agentcube_provider.py`\n**Status:** EXISTS - has `get_agent_runtime()` method (lines 115-135)\n- 135 lines total\n- `get_agent_runtime(name)` retrieves an AgentRuntime CR by name, returns `None` on 404\n- Does NOT have invoke-specific methods\n\n### 3. `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py`\n**Status:** EXISTS - but does NOT have `get_agent_status()` method\n- 205 lines total\n- Has: `deploy_agent()`, `wait_for_deployment_ready()`, `delete_agent()`\n- Missing: `get_agent_status()` (planned for status command)\n\n### 4. `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/__init__.py`\n**Status:** EXISTS - exports only `PackRuntime`, `BuildRuntime`, `PublishRuntime`\n- No `InvokeRuntime` or `StatusRuntime` exports\n\n### 5. `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/publish_runtime.py`\n**Status:** EXISTS - reference implementation showing the pattern invoke/status would follow\n- 216 lines total\n- Shows provider selection pattern (`agentcube` vs `k8s`)\n\n---\n\n## Files That DO NOT EXIST\n\n| Planned File | Status |\n|---|---|\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/invoke_runtime.py` | **DOES NOT EXIST** |\n| `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/status_runtime.py` | **DOES NOT EXIST** |\n| `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_invoke_runtime.py` | **DOES NOT EXIST** |\n| `cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_status_runtime.py` | **DOES NOT EXIST** |\n| `cmd/cli/tests/cli/test_invoke_command.py` | **DOES NOT EXIST** |\n| `cmd/cli/tests/cli/test_status_command.py` | **DOES NOT EXIST** |\n\n---\n\n## Specification Documents (Planned Implementation)\n\n### `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/delta-spec.md`\nFull delta spec (273 lines) defining:\n- **invoke command**: POSTs JSON payload to agent endpoint, supports `--payload`, `--header`, `--provider`\n- **status command**: Loads metadata, displays Rich Table with agent status\n- **InvokeRuntime class**: `invoke()`, `_validate_invoke_prerequisites()`, `_invoke_agent_via_agentcube()`, `_direct_http_invocation()`\n- **StatusRuntime class**: `get_status()`, `_get_cr_k8s_status()`, `_get_k8s_status()`\n\n### `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/proposal.md`\nFull proposal (232 lines) with implementation code snippets for both commands.\n\n### `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/design.md`\nDesign doc (62 lines) with component signatures.\n\n### `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-023/tasks.md`\nTask list (108 lines) - all tasks unchecked:\n- T1: Implement InvokeRuntime class\n- T2: Enhance StatusRuntime class\n- T3: Implement CLI invoke command\n- T4: Implement CLI status command\n- T5: Code quality gates\n\n### `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cli-toolkit/spec.md`\nFull CLI specification (197 lines) including invoke/status requirements.\n\n---\n\n## Existing Test Files (for reference patterns)\n\n| Test File | Path |\n|---|---|\n| PublishRuntime tests | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/tests/runtime/test_publish_runtime.py` |\n| AgentCubeProvider tests | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/tests/services/test_agentcube_provider.py` |\n| K8sProvider tests | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/tests/services/test_k8s_provider.py` |\n| Build command tests | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/cmd/cli/tests/cli/test_build_command.py` |\n\n---\n\n## What Needs to Be Implemented\n\nBased on the specs, the following code needs to be created:\n\n1. **`invoke_runtime.py`** - `InvokeRuntime` class with:\n   - `__init__(self, verbose: bool = False, provider: str = \"agentcube\")`\n   - `invoke(workspace_path, payload, headers)` - main method\n   - `_validate_invoke_prerequisites(workspace_path)` - validates metadata\n   - `_invoke_agent_via_agentcube(...)` - AgentRuntime CR invocation with URL rewriting\n   - `_direct_http_invocation(...)` - direct HTTP POST\n\n2. **`status_runtime.py`** - `StatusRuntime` class with:\n   - `__init__(self, verbose: bool = False, provider: str = \"agentcube\")`\n   - `get_status(workspace_path, provider)` - main method\n   - `_get_cr_k8s_status(metadata)` - query AgentRuntime CR status\n   - `_get_k8s_status(metadata)` - query standard K8s deployment status\n\n3. **`main.py` additions** - Two new `@app.command()` functions:\n   - `invoke()` - with `--workspace`, `--payload`, `--header`, `--provider`, `--verbose`\n   - `status()` - with `--workspace`, `--provider`, `--verbose`\n\n4. **`k8s_provider.py` addition** - `get_agent_status(agent_name)` method\n\n5. **Test files** - Four new test files following existing patterns\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_286be54ceffeYl7uK1tpbR3xQ7","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore invoke/status source code","time":{"start":1775855840047,"end":1775855944272}}}}
